The Team

A successful 项目文档requires many people to play many roles. Some members write code or documentation, while others are valuable as testers, submitting patches and suggestions.

The team is comprised of Members and Contributors. Members have direct access to the source of a 项目文档and actively evolve the code-base. Contributors improve the 项目文档through submission of patches and suggestions to the Members. The number of Contributors to the 项目文档is unbounded. Get involved today. All contributions to the 项目文档are greatly appreciated.
